<section class="pillars-section" aria-labelledby="pillars-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="pillars-grid" data-gsap="stagger">
      <!-- Community -->
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-kicker">
          <span class="pillar-rule" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          Community
        </div>
        <h3 class="pillar-heading" id="pillars-heading">Photography becomes meaningful when shared.</h3>
        <p class="pillar-body">Here, beginners find mentors and experienced photographers find fresh inspiration. No one arrives at their best work alone. Learning happens in the open — on the street, beside a lake, in front of a monument — together. BCC is the community that makes this possible in Bhopal.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Craft -->
      <div class="pillar-card pillar-card--alt">
        <div class="pillar-kicker">
          <span class="pillar-rule" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          Craft
        </div>
        <h3 class="pillar-heading">Photography is both art and discipline.</h3>
        <p class="pillar-body">Through photowalks, workshops, critiques and talks, members develop not just technical skill but creative intention — a distinct way of seeing. The club is a place where a beginner photographer can become a serious one, and where a serious photographer can always find something new to learn.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- City -->
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-kicker">
          <span class="pillar-rule" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          City
        </div>
        <h3 class="pillar-heading">Bhopal is our greatest teacher.</h3>
        <p class="pillar-body">Its lakes, its forests, its architecture, its festivals, its people across changing seasons — BCC has been building a visual archive of this extraordinary city since 2015. Lakes at golden dawn. Van Vihar in winter. The Old City in monsoon light. Bhopal rewards the patient photographer abundantly.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.pillars-section {
  background: var(--surface-0);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline);
}
.pillars-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
  border: 1px solid var(--hairline);
  background: var(--surface-0);
}
.pillar-card {
  padding: 48px 40px;
  border-right: 1px solid var(--hairline);
}
.pillar-card:last-child {
  border-right: none;
}
.pillar-card--alt {
  background: var(--surface-1);
}
.pillar-kicker {
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.22em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold-600);
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
  font-family: var(--font-body);
}
.pillar-rule {
  display: block;
  width: 16px;
  height: 1px;
  background: var(--gold-500);
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.pillar-heading {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 26px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: -0.015em;
  line-height: 1.1;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  color: var(--ink-900);
}
.pillar-body {
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 1.9;
  color: var(--ink-600);
}

/* Responsive */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .pillars-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  .pillar-card {
    border-right: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    padding: 36px 28px;
  }
  .pillar-card:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
}
</style>
